org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.impl

Class PullEventsImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.impl.PullEventsImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Documentable, PullEvents

    public class PullEventsImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements PullEvents
    An implementation of the model object 'Pull Events'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Short Description
    • Name
    • Jdbc Driver Name
    • Jdbc Properties
    • Job Interval
    • Custom Select Sql
    • Custom Delete Sql
